    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Our Team</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8">
          Behind every product is a team of dedicated professionals committed to excellence. From our skilled engineers to our quality control specialists, every member of the Raytron family plays a vital role in delivering the highest quality flat wire solutions.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">
          We invest in continuous training and development to ensure our team stays at the forefront of flat wire manufacturing technology and customer service excellence.
